 "lrc": "[00:00.00]Morning light...\n[00:12.56]Take me there...\n[00:19.34]Take me there...\n[00:29.27](instrumental)\n[00:32.57]Leaves above, the river below\n[00:49.12]Every little heartbeat moving slow\n[00:51.22]Hands in the breeze\n[00:52.96]Nothing to chase\n[00:54.56]Time disappears without a trace\n[00:57.36]Hold me\n[00:58.64]Don't let go\n[01:01.92]Where we wander\n[01:03.84]Flowers grow\n[01:05.44]Days drift by\n[01:10.23]We don't have to know why\n[01:13.80]Breathe tonight\n[01:14.88]Everything feels alive\n[01:21.70]Days drift by\n[01:32.45]Floating into the sky\n[01:43.68]Stay with me\n[01:45.14]Stay with me\n[01:46.59]Stay...\n[01:47.07](Liquid DnB instrumental with melodic lead and guitar textures)\n[01:51.43]Clouds roll in\n[01:52.88]Then fade away\n[01:54.48]Every color melts into gray\n[01:56.88]Then the sun\n[01:57.92]Finds its way\n[02:00.32]Just like it always does\n[02:03.36]Closer...\n[02:04.88]Closer...\n[02:06.08]Into the light...\n[02:11.52]Higher...\n[02:11.52]Higher...\n[02:11.52]Through the leaves...\n[02:12.64](Long instrumental featuring evolving pads, liquid breaks, melodic synth lead, and shimmering guitar)\n[02:25.09]Days drift by\n[02:44.67]We don't have to know why\n[02:51.60]Breathe tonight\n[02:51.60]Everything feels alive\n[02:51.60]Days drift by\n[02:51.60]Floating into the sky\n[02:51.60]Stay with me\n[02:52.80]Stay with me\n[02:55.12]Days drift by...\n[03:08.24]Days drift by...\n[03:08.32]Days drift by...\n[03:08.32](Fade into rainforest ambience and distant vocal echoes.)\n"
